OmG what a singing. kudos to Piyush Mishra and the musicians 👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻it could not have been better than this. I heard this song for the first time yesterday and I had goosebumps. So deep, so touching and yet so soothing. I was deeply lost in song  and could feel every words sung and every instrument played. . It’s 3:32 am in India and Husna made me wake up and listen to Husna again. Dying to sing this song. Please help me with this music🙏🏻
